metadata.name: OKAY Token #2
metadata.description: OKAY V2 is a collection of 302 unique NFTs (Non-Fungible Tokens) that truly focuses on the meme culture of web 3.0. OKAY NFT V2 is supported by our native token: OKAY which is the first original OKAY token launched on the Ethereum blockchain. V2 is also supported our first generation OkayNFT. Holding enough OKAY NFT V2 will give you a special utility that correlates with our native token and to Yako club (an exclusive member for gen 1 holders only).
